headline: The J.M. Smucker Co. Announces Senior Leadership Updates to Drive Continued Growth and Execution
summary: The J.M. Smucker Co. today announced a series of leadership updates that are designed to advance the Company's continued execution of its long-term growth strategy and further the momentum of its portfolio of leading brands, while enhancing profitability and earnings.
